| tstats count min(_time) as firstTime max(_time) as lastTime
    from datamodel=Authentication.Authentication
    where Authentication.action=success
    by Authentication.user Authentication.src_ip
| rename Authentication.* as *
| stats values(src_ip) as src_ips count by user
| where mvcount(src_ips) > 1
| eval risk="Possible account sharing or credential theft"
| table user src_ips count risk firstTime lastTime
| sort - count

| MITRE:     T1078 - Valid Accounts
| Tactic:    Initial Access, Persistence
| Platform:  Splunk (CIM Authentication datamodel)
| Threshold: Tune mvcount value based on environment
| FP notes:  VPN split-tunneling, mobile + desktop same user
